'''白俄羅斯航空'''（{{lang-be|'''Белавія'''}}；{{lang-ru|'''Белавиа'''}}；{{lang-en|'''Belavia'''}}）是[[白俄羅斯|白俄羅斯]]的[[國家航空公司|國家航空公司]]，總部位於[[明斯克|明斯克]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://en.belavia.by/contacts/|title = Belavia website: Contacts|publisher = En.belavia.by|date = |accessdate = 2013-02-04|archive-date = 2021-11-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211115001114/https://en.belavia.by/contacts/|dead-url = no}}</ref>公司擁有1,017名員工，<ref name="FI">{{Cite news|title = Directory: World Airlines|work = [[Flight_International|Flight International]]|pages = 84–85|date = 2007-03-27}}</ref>提供連接[[明斯克国际机场|明斯克国际机场]]與歐洲和[[獨立國家聯合體|獨立國家聯合體]]的航班服務，以及部分中東航線。<ref name="FI"/>

2021年5月24日，英國暫停白俄羅斯航空的運營許可，作為對[[瑞安航空4978號班機事件|瑞安航空4978號班機事件]]的回應。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-05-24|title=UK's Raab says Lukashenko must be held to account for jet incident|url=https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/uks-raab-says-lukashenko-must-be-held-account-jet-incident-2021-05-24/|access-date=2021-05-24|website=Reuters|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524151546/https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/uks-raab-says-lukashenko-must-be-held-account-jet-incident-2021-05-24/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨後歐盟也禁止白俄羅斯的航空公司使用其領空和機場。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-05-25|script-title=en:EU imposes new economic sanctions on Belarus over ‘hijacked’ flight|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/may/24/belarus-put-on-notice-of-sanctions-over-hijack-of-ryanair-flight|access-date=2021-05-25|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221180307/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/may/24/belarus-put-on-notice-of-sanctions-over-hijack-of-ryanair-flight|dead-url=no}}</ref>

